sources.title: Rio Diablo | FULL MOVIE | Action, Western | Kenny Rogers, Travis Tritt, Naomi Judd, Stacy Keach
sources.description:
A bounty hunter with an unsavory past is on the trail of a gang of murdering bank robbers. He's joined by a naive farmer whose sweet young bride has been kidnapped and taken hostage by the odious outlaws.

Kenny Rogers
Travis Tritt
Naomi Judd
Brion James
Bruce Greenwood
Laura Harring
Stacy Keach

1993
Directed by Rod Hardy

Action
Western
Drama
Mystery
Adventure
